&lt;p&gt;This is a new Pharmacy Technician role working across a group of GP Practices within the Banes area. The primary purpose of the role is to support the practice team in managing on-the-day urgent medication queries and requests (further details on attached Job Description).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Postholder will be able to access the NHS Pension Scheme.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;BEMS is a not-for-profit Community Mutual Provider, whose members include local GPs and practices as well as staff and patients. It supplies NHS services that are free to all Bath &amp; North East Somerset Patients.&lt;/p&gt;
